{"tid":1815931,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有區議員發現到荃灣梨木樹同沙田廣源清牆係同一批人","createTime":"2020-01-08T01:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T01:42:02.000Z","uid":63667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2a9b6afaa40340d2c13e2a65f9caf117018525","tid":1815931,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101654267923008/posts/148371146584653/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101654267923008%2Fposts%2F148371146584653%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=d920cdf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101654267923008/posts/148371146584653/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"a2ff017ebc09c4fed79edf810ff83d74c1f47263","tid":1815931,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffad8c81a016c8dce4e2c1d18540b48cfc74198","tid":1815931,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d2a9b6afaa40340d2c13e2a65f9caf117018525","tid":1815931,"uid":63667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101654267923008/posts/148371146584653/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101654267923008%2Fposts%2F148371146584653%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=d920cdf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101654267923008/posts/148371146584653/?d=n</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfscZFL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfscZFL.jpg&h=778acf14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>18區區議會</strong></ins><br />\n每區區議會需在該區人流就多既位置，<strong>安裝正式既連農文宣牆 (情況有如廣告箱)，</strong> <br />\n同時安排保安公司管理。 費用就香港人既錢(公帑)支付。<br />\n<br />\n以上工程，由黃色工程公司負責，當中可請手足full / part time幫手。<br />\n對家用呢重方法玩咗廿幾年，今次到香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>[不同政見，都可以提交文宣]</strong></ins><br />\n機會平等，所有人都可以將文宣交到當區區議員手上<br />\n佢地會有既定「機制」去分類放上連農<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>我地要好好理用手上 區議會權力同資源</ins></strong><br />\n- 18-1區文宣正式化<br />\n- 擴大及鞏固黃色經濟圈<br />\n- 支援手足 保護手足<br />\n<br />\n「18區議會入」港共自己都係行人隧道做文宣 我地點解唔可以？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813044</a>"}]}